WEBVTT

00:09:01.633 --> 00:09:05.151
We, scientists --
You see that I'm struggling here

00:09:05.151 --> 00:09:07.634
to move my head
from one side to the other.

00:09:07.634 --> 00:09:13.031
Scientists study how it works, why, etc.

00:09:13.031 --> 00:09:17.718
and these studies
are generating a series of discoveries,

00:09:17.718 --> 00:09:19.290
which are absolutely fabulous,

00:09:19.290 --> 00:09:22.283
to raise our awareness of the wealth,

00:09:22.283 --> 00:09:24.668
the complexity,
and the wonder that we have,

00:09:24.668 --> 00:09:27.649
the symphony we have in this process.

00:09:27.649 --> 00:09:29.997
One of them is: How is rain formed?

00:09:29.997 --> 00:09:33.522
Above the Amazon, there is clean air,